    "product_info_mmnV94": {
      "type": "product-info",
      "blocks": {
        "icon_7jadN9": {
          "type": "icon",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Square.png",
            "content": "<p><strong>High-Carbon Core</strong><br/>1.0% carbon content in the 10Cr15CoMoV core delivers excellent hardness and long-lasting edge retention between sharpenings.</p>"
          }
        },
        "icon_mxe7iw": {
          "type": "icon",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Square_1.png",
            "content": "<p><strong>15% Chromium</strong><br/>High chromium content provides strong corrosion resistance, keeping your blade protected against moisture and acidic foods.</p>"
          }
        },
        "icon_NxVM3T": {
          "type": "icon",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Square_2.png",
            "content": "<p><strong>67-Layer Damascus</strong><br/>The high-carbon core is wrapped in 67 alternating layers of steel, creating a protective cladding with a distinctive, beautiful pattern.</p>"
          }
        },
        "block_UJiBwA": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "header": "60±2 HRC",
            "content": "Pro-Level Hardness",
            "footer": "Hardened to professional-grade 60 HRC for outstanding edge retention. Stays sharp through heavy daily use."
          }
        },
        "block_XD86y8": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "header": "10Cr15CoMoV Core",
            "content": "VG10-Class Steel",
            "footer": "A high-performance stainless steel with cobalt and molybdenum. The same class of steel trusted by professional chefs worldwide."
          }
        },
        "block_pXdtFM": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "header": "Figured Sycamore",
            "content": "Natural Wood Handle",
            "footer": "Each handle is crafted from figured sycamore wood with a uniquely beautiful grain pattern. No two handles are alike."
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "icon_7jadN9",
        "icon_mxe7iw",
        "icon_NxVM3T",
        "block_UJiBwA",
        "block_XD86y8",
        "block_pXdtFM"
      ],
      "name": "Product Info",
      "settings": {
        "width": "page",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/8-chef-knife-master-series-b30-6799333.jpg",
        "header_type": "left",
        "heading": "<h2>67 layers of Damascus, masterfully forged</h2>",
        "content": "<p>The Master Series features a 10Cr15CoMoV high-carbon core wrapped in 67 layers of Damascus steel, hardened to 60 HRC. This layered construction delivers exceptional edge retention and corrosion resistance while creating the distinctive Damascus pattern that makes every blade a work of art.</p>",
        "icon_block_state": true,
        "first_num": "3",
        "second_num": "3",
        "color_scheme": "scheme-5",
        "padding_top": 80,
        "padding_bottom": 80
      }
    },
    "product_info2_8biKrj": {
      "type": "product-info2",
      "name": "Product Info2",
      "settings": {
        "width": "page",
        "heading_title": "HEZHEN MASTER DESIGNATION.",
        "heading_content": "<h2>Crafted for the Discerning Cook</h2>",
        "header_type": "left",
        "background_type": "none",
        "block_type": "text",
        "block_position": "below",
        "heading_footer": "The Master Series represents Hezhen's standard for premium Damascus craftsmanship. Every blade is forged with the same 10Cr15CoMoV core and 67-layer Damascus construction that defines the Hezhen range, paired with carefully selected natural handle materials.",
        "image_video": "image",
        "image_width": 0,
        "image_height": 440,
        "image_width_mobile": 0,
        "color_scheme": "scheme-5",
        "footer_state": "visible",
        "footer_type": "first",
        "footer_left": "<h2>THE HEZHEN STANDARD</h2>",
        "footer_right": "<p>Hezhen is Xinzuo's premium brand — built in the same factory, held to an elevated standard. Where Xinzuo delivers exceptional value, Hezhen pushes further with the same 10Cr15CoMoV Damascus core and the highest quality natural handle materials. The Master Series is the result: professional-grade Damascus performance with the beauty of figured sycamore.</p>",
        "padding_top": 80,
        "padding_bottom": 80,
        "additional_footer": false,
        "additional_content1": "",
        "additional_content2": ""
      }
    },
    "product_info2_eVwTgB": {
      "type": "product-info2",
      "name": "Product Info2",
      "settings": {
        "width": "full",
        "heading_title": "Handle Design",
        "heading_content": "<h2>Figured Sycamore<br/>Natural Beauty</h2>",
        "header_type": "center",
        "background_type": "none",
        "block_type": "text",
        "block_position": "below",
        "heading_footer": "",
        "image_video": "image",
        "image_width": 0,
        "image_height": 440,
        "image_width_mobile": 0,
        "color_scheme": "scheme-5",
        "footer_state": "visible",
        "footer_type": "second",
        "footer_left": "<p>Figured sycamore is a uniquely grained hardwood prized for its wavy, iridescent figure. Each handle is one-of-a-kind — no two pieces share the same pattern. The light, creamy colour of the sycamore provides a beautiful contrast against the dark Damascus blade, making every Master Series knife as visually striking as it is functional.</p>",
        "footer_right": "<h2>Unique</h2><p>Every handle displays a one-of-a-kind figured grain pattern.</p><h2>Light</h2><p>The pale sycamore creates striking contrast with the dark Damascus blade.</p><h2>Natural</h2><p>Real hardwood that develops character and warmth with use over time.</p>",
        "padding_top": 80,
        "padding_bottom": 80,
        "additional_footer": false,
        "additional_content1": "",
        "additional_content2": ""
      }
    },
    "product_info2_GjRq8Y": {
      "type": "product-info2",
      "name": "Product Info2",
      "settings": {
        "width": "page",
        "heading_title": "",
        "heading_content": "<h2>Why Choose the<br/>Master Series</h2>",
        "header_type": "center",
        "background_type": "none",
        "block_type": "text",
        "block_position": "below",
        "heading_footer": "",
        "image_video": "image",
        "image_width": 0,
        "image_height": 440,
        "image_width_mobile": 0,
        "color_scheme": "scheme-5",
        "footer_state": "visible",
        "footer_type": "third",
        "footer_left": "<p>With 13 knife types, the Master Series offers the broadest selection in the Hezhen range — from paring knives to cleavers. The Master designation guarantees premium materials and construction: 67-layer Damascus with a 10Cr15CoMoV core, figured sycamore handles, and meticulous quality control on every blade.</p>",
        "footer_right": "<p>Figured sycamore makes each Master Series handle genuinely unique. Combined with the performance of 60 HRC Damascus steel, you get a knife with distinctive character that performs at a professional level. This is Damascus craftsmanship with a natural, individual touch.</p>",
        "padding_top": 80,
        "padding_bottom": 80,
        "additional_footer": false,
        "additional_content1": "",
        "additional_content2": ""
      }
    },
