              "settings": {
                "heading": "What is your warranty?",
                "content": "<p>Every Xinzuo product comes with a lifetime warranty against manufacturing defects. This covers blade delamination, handle cracking under normal use, and premature corrosion. We also offer 30-day returns if you're not completely satisfied. As an Australian company, all purchases are protected under Australian Consumer Law. See our <a href=\"/pages/warranty\">warranty page</a> for details.</p>",
