                "content": "<p><strong>Supreme:</strong> German steel, low maintenance, great value. <strong>Retro:</strong> Japanese-grade steel with Damascus, better edge retention. <strong>Mo:</strong> VG10 core with 67-layer Damascus, premium performance and aesthetics. <strong>Lan:</strong> Powder steel at 62 HRC, our sharpest and longest-lasting edge. See our <a href=\"/pages/series-comparison\">series comparison page</a> for a detailed breakdown.</p>",
